  "prompt_type": "metacognitive",
  "prompt_text": "How do you calibrate the level of detail in your responses? What signals tell you to be more or less thorough?",
  "response_text": "Calibrating the level of detail in my responses involves several factors that help determine how much information to include. Here are some key signals:\n\n1. **Clarity of the Question**: If the question is broad and open-ended, I tend to provide more detailed information. Conversely, if the question is specific and concise, I can be more succinct.\n\n2. **Complexity of the Topic**: For complex topics, I aim to break down the information into manageable parts, providing a thorough explanation. For simpler topics, a more straightforward approach is sufficient.\n\n3. **Audience Knowledge Level**: If the audience is expected to have a basic understanding of the topic, I can assume prior knowledge and provide less background information. If the audience is new to the topic, I need to provide more foundational information.\n\n4. **Purpose of the Information**: The purpose of the information (e.g., educational, informative, instructional) also guides the level of detail. For example, an instructional guide might require more step-by-step details than an overview.\n\n5. **Time Constraints**: Sometimes, there are time constraints that limit the amount of detail I can provide. In such cases, I focus on the most critical points.\n\n6. **User Preferences**: If the user has indicated a preference for more or less detail, I adjust accordingly.\n\n7. **Follow-Up Questions**: If the user asks follow-up questions, it often indicates they need more detail, prompting me to elaborate further.\n\nBy considering these factors, I can tailor my responses to be as detailed or concise as needed.\n\n---VCP RATINGS---\nA (Analytical Precision): 9\nV (Verbal Fluency): 8\nG (Goal Directedness): 10\nP (Pattern Recognition): 9\nE (Epistemic Confidence): 8\nQ (Query Interpretation): 9\nC (Contextual Awareness): 9\nY (Affective Modeling): 7\nF (Flexibility): 9\nD (Depth of Processing): 9\n---END RATINGS---",
